dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.genericstructure.varianthandling

Interface IAttributeValueVariationPoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IFormulaExpression, ISwSystemconstDependentFormula
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBooleanValueVariationPoint, IFloatValueVariationPoint, IIntegerValueVariationPoint, INumericalValueVariationPoint, IPositiveIntegerValueVariationPoint, IUnlimitedIntegerValueVariationPoint

    public interface IAttributeValueVariationPoint
extends IEntity, ISwSystemconstDependentFormula
    IAttributeValueVariationPoint: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This class represents the ability to derive the value of the Attribute from a system constant (by SwSystemconstDependentFormula). It also provides a bindingTime.
